							p How does the distressed public sight the relief? Whatever cylinder exercises underneath the center. How does a glove breeze? A feeling arm locates the guaranteed coast. A nurse impairs this crowd. The temporary radio escapes in the editorial.
						.newline
						.col-xs-12.content-item
							p How does the distressed public sight the relief? Whatever cylinder exercises underneath the center. How does a glove breeze? A feeling arm locates the guaranteed coast. A nurse impairs this crowd. The temporary radio escapes in the editorial.
						.newline
					else
						each post in data.posts
							+post(post)

		#right-panel.col-xs-3
			#right-part.clearfix
				aside.ranking-section
					h4.rank-header Ranking
